msgid "Add web-server rules (Apache/LiteSpeed) to block common threats."
msgstr "Web-server regels (Apache/LiteSpeed) toevoegen om veelvoorkomende bedreigingen te blokkeren."

#: classes/wp-security-onboarding.php:487
msgid "Pre-load firewall rules"
msgstr "Voordat de firewallregels worden geladen"

